## ğŸ” API Endpoints

| Endpoint                   | Method | Description                  |
|---------------------------|--------|------------------------------|
| `/api/predict`            | POST   | Predict fraud from data      |
| `/api/report-stolen`      | POST   | Mark card as stolen          |
| `/api/get-transactions`   | GET    | Retrieve transaction logs    |

